 143.1293, 144.2371, 144.1507, 143.9779, 143.0931, 142.2642, 142.6255, 142.9126, 141.5891, 142.7331, 143.3806, 143.596, 144.1416, 143.0131, 143.2012, 141.3876, 140.5084, 141.3135, 141.3277, 141.858, 142.7318, 141.9769, 142.981, 144.0883, 143.9156, 143.4956, 141.8487, 142.2807, 142.9878, 142.5704, 143.7852, 143.6452, 141.9485, 139.8068, 139.328, 138.5271, 139.6614, 139.179, 140.366, 137.9258, 136.9995, 137.738, 137.1401, 137.6958, 138.6428, 137.9321, 138.9821, 139.2452, 138.9479, 140.0039, 140.855, 140.1573, 139.9009, 137.954, 139.4627, 140.1449, 141.5293, 141.15, 143.9087, 144.4861, 146.3851, 146.8119, 147.4311, 146.8848, 147.3946, 147.7434, 147.9158, 147.7749, 147.1223, 147.7471, 148.8056, 148.33, 146.5412, 142.3782, 143.4304, 141.0115, 140.0777, 140.3505, 140.3959, 142.0999, 142.9308, 142.8736, 142.3513, 142.7846, 143.5668, 142.8034, 143.9864, 144.0038, 144.55, 143.6897, 143.5837, 143.8541, 144.4466, 143.2944, 143.2159, 145.3539, 145.7087, 145.4374, 144.8418, 145.232, 145.6622, 145.0925, 145.3509, 144.1944, 145.9867, 146.4993, 147.3398, 148.403, 148.8181, 149.6625, 149.4991, 147.9534, 148.3521, 147.8153, 147.2905, 147.5295, 147.9773, 148.1644, 149.9937, 150.2866, 151.0221, 152.3684, 153.6989, 153.1868, 152.8188, 149.0658, 149.0519, 148.5726, 148.8775, 147.5202, 147.3929, 150.9894, 150.5681, 150.3451, 150.4822, 151.07, 151.1785, 152.1222, 152.2442, 152.4543, 152.6142, 152.6175, 152.9083, 151.661, 152.0925, 153.3728, 153.4482, 154.3844, 152.7243, 152.1241, 153.065, 151.7247, 152.5005, 151.9165, 150.42, 151.3464, 151.9486, 151.6183, 152.465, 153.547, 154.5027, 154.8212, 154.8679, 156.3426, 157.3701, 156.8906, 156.5093, 157.3253, 158.1847, 159.7283, 159.6375, 159.6313, 159.5281, 159.5197, 160.2135, 160.6402, 161.3518, 160.9948, 161.4387, 161.0018, 161.2815, 160.2729, 160.848, 161.5034, 161.2407, 161.8115, 160.5008, 159.6871, 159.9597, 158.4323, 158.453, 157.9454, 157.3381, 157.8265, 158.4438, 159.4282, 159.3916, 158.536, 158.4643, 157.6396, 158.8085, 158.4649, 159.9247, 160.9283, 159.6126, 159.0223, 159.6434, 159.7693, 158.8898, 158.43, 160.0734, 159.1, 159.2188, 159.317, 159.389, 160.4808, 160.2204, 160.4904, 160.7812, 162.5375, 162.9332, 164.3941, 163.293, 162.0471, 163.559, 164.0171, 164.278, 163.1808, 162.785, 163.0735, 162.9001, 162.2128, 162.643, 162.6815, 163.1166, 164.275, 164.0802, 165.7891, 166.0928, 168.0375, 168.9672, 170.0779, 171.842, 169.1914, 169.8715, 171.0123, 169.6149, 168.1531, 167.5582, 169.7247, 170.1627, 170.3154, 169.9012, 168.9958, 169.3041, 169.0581, 169.4021, 168.2904, 169.8317, 172.2349, 172.2294, 173.2818, 174.1401, 176.032, 175.8218, 175.2847, 174.9353, 176.5603, 177.7503, 177.2702, 178.0388, 179.6106, 181.1753, 181.6864, 181.2567, 181.3847, 182.114, 180.6729, 179.0682, 180.2316, 178.1736, 178.4504, 177.6895, 176.381, 176.5594, 176.5397, 175.94, 176.5496, 175.5759, 175.3558, 172.2586, 169.7297, 171.027, 169.6767, 172.0039, 179.9258, 172.1862, 176.7578, 178.4177, 178.0654, 178.9163, 179.7228, 179.8775, 181.4249, 182.4297, 183.5282, 183.9499, 181.7235, 182.5266, 183.2805, 183.6618, 182.9063, 183.6901, 183.8302, 185.3456, 187.8365, 184.762, 186.7347, 183.9749, 184.5824, 185.1938, 184.9528, 184.6394, 186.0528, 185.3042, 184.0132, 184.676, 184.2175, 184.3526, 184.5641, 184.3885, 185.0549, 185.7345, 186.2841, 185.7057, 186.1177, 187.565, 187.1654, 186.8515, 186.6959, 186.32, 186.3404, 186.6011, 185.9607, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>主动买卖单的批量成交划分法 (BVC)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>原报告（东方证券 朱剑涛，针对股票市场）提出批量成交划分法 (Bulk Volume Classification, BVC, ELO 2012)，从分钟 K 线估算每个 bar 的主动买入占比，无需逐笔委托数据，通过每分钟价格变动的标准化值和 t 分布 CDF 推断买卖方向，降低高频环境中订单拆分带来的噪声。报告在股票上构造净主买占比 (OI) 与净换手率 (NTO) 因子，呈反转特征（高值未来收益低）。</p>\n<p>本复现把这套测度迁移到<strong>中国商品期货截面</strong>，并发现方向在商品上<strong>翻转为动量</strong>。实盘生产变体 <code>oi_bvc_5_raw</code> 的信号构造严格如下（<code>strategy_final.py</code>，全程因果）：</p>\n<p>1. 用 <code>get_minute_data()</code> 取分钟 K 线（sym/datetime/close/volume），一个 <code>@njit(parallel=True)</code> 核按 (sym, date) 分组单遍计算每个 bar 的价差 <code>dp = close.diff()</code>、当日 <code>dp</code> 的标准差 <code>sigma_dp</code>（ddof=1）、以及 BVC 买入占比 <code>buy_pct</code>，再聚合出当日 <code>bvc_bvol = Σ vol·buy_pct</code>、<code>bvc_svol = Σ vol·(1-buy_pct)</code>、<code>total_vol = Σ vol</code>；当日有效 bar ≤ 10 的日丢弃。 2. 与日频 OPI universe（<code>opi &gt; 0</code>）按 (sym, date) inner-join，构造<strong>净主买占比</strong> <code>oi_bvc_daily = (bvc_bvol - bvc_svol) / total_vol</code>。 3. 每品种 <strong>5 日滚动均值</strong> <code>oi_bvc_5</code>（<code>min_periods=3</code>）。 4. <code>cs_factor_to_position(oi_bvc_5, hold=5, vt=0.15)</code>：截面百分位排名 <code>cr_rank</code> → <code>rank_to_continuous(scale=+2.0)</code>（<strong>动量方向：高净主买做多、低净主买做空</strong>）→ 波动率目标缩放（vol_target=0.15, max_lev=2.0, vol_window=60）→ <code>rebalance_hold(hold_days=5)</code>。</p>\n<p><strong>关键发现</strong>：(1) 方向相对原股票报告<strong>翻转</strong>——商品上净主买是动量而非反转（早期按反转 scale=-2 复现全亏，R2 翻成 +2 后跳升）；(2) 报告/spec 中提到的 <code>sym_rolling_ic_gate</code> 在原 polars 实现里 rank 用的是原始因子列而非 gate 输出，是 no-op，生产 pandas 版据此<strong>不启用 IC gate</strong>（见 audit.md）；(3) 因子非冗余（max_corr≈0.23）。</p>\n<p><strong>防前视</strong>：<code>dp</code> 仅用同 sym 前一根有效 bar 的 close 差分；<code>oi_bvc_5</code> 为因果滚动均值；OPI 取当日值；position 经 <code>rebalance_hold</code> 后于次日开盘执行。生产代码不读 <code>level2_all</code>/NTO 等分支（spec 中的 L2/NTO/abs 变体均未采用）。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.13</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.1%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.6%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-7.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.28</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2515</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.03</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.9</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.91 / 1.14</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.47</td><td>1.5</td><td>0.7</td><td>0.1</td><td>1.55</td><td>1.74</td><td>0.53</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.41</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.53</span></td><td>1.7</td><td>1.73</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>volume</code></td><td>成交量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>opi</code></td><td>持仓量</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 5 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 5 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2517</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>45.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>BVC 主动买入占比（每分钟bar）：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">V_B^\\tau = \\Phi_t\\left(\\frac{P_t - P_{t-1}}{\\sigma_{\\Delta P}},\\, df=0.25\\right)</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\Phi_t</span> 为 t 分布的累积分布函数，<span class=\"math-tex\">P_t - P_{t-1}</span> 为相邻分钟bar的收盘价差，<span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_{\\Delta P}</span> 为当日所有分钟价差的标准差，<span class=\"math-tex\">df=0.25</span> 为自由度（原文献推荐值）。实现中使用 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CDF} \\approx 0.5 + \\frac{1}{\\pi}\\arctan(z\\sqrt{\\nu})</span> 近似。</p>\n<p><strong>日度主动买卖量聚合（对每个 (sym, 交易日 d) 内的所有有效分钟 bar 求和）：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">V_b^d = \\sum_{\\tau \\in d} V^\\tau \\cdot V_B^\\tau, \\quad V_s^d = \\sum_{\\tau \\in d} V^\\tau \\cdot (1 - V_B^\\tau), \\quad V_{\\rm tot}^d = \\sum_{\\tau \\in d} V^\\tau</div>\n<p>由构造有 <span class=\"math-tex\">V_b^d + V_s^d = V_{\\rm tot}^d</span>。</p>\n<p><strong>净主买占比日因子（生产用）：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{oi\\_bvc\\_daily}^d = \\frac{V_b^d - V_s^d}{V_{\\rm tot}^d}</div>\n<p><strong>5 日滚动均值（最终因子，<code>min_periods</code>=3）：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{oi\\_bvc\\_5}_t = \\frac{1}{5}\\sum_{i=0}^{4}\\text{oi\\_bvc\\_daily}_{t-i}</div>\n<p><strong>仓位（<code>cs_factor_to_position</code>）：</strong>截面百分位排名后映射成 <span class=\"math-tex\">[-1,1]</span> 连续多空（scale=+2，高值做多），再 vol-target 缩放到 15% 年化（<span class=\"math-tex\">L_{\\max}=2</span>）、5 日 rebalance：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{pos}_t^{(s)} = \\operatorname{rebalance\\_hold}_5\\!\\Big(\\operatorname{clip}\\big(\\text{cont}(\\text{rank}_t(\\text{oi\\_bvc\\_5}))\\cdot \\tfrac{\\sigma_{tgt}}{\\hat\\sigma_{60}\\sqrt{252}},\\ \\pm 2\\big)\\Big)</div>\n<blockquote>注：spec 中另有净换手率 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{NTO}=(V_b-V_s)/\\text{OPI}</span> 及其 L2 / |·| 变体，但<strong>均非实盘采用</strong>；生产仅 <code>oi_bvc_5</code>。</blockquote>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1</strong> -- 信号方向错误导致失败</p>\n<ul><li>诊断: 假设因子IC为负（股票反转逻辑），所有OI/NTO变体Sharpe为-0.7~-1.4，仅NTO_abs(非方向性)有微弱正Sharpe 0.15</li>\n<li>行动: 无（识别出根因）</li>\n<li>效果: Sharpe 0.15, backtest gate失败</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>R2</strong> -- 修正信号方向，Sharpe跃升至1.39</p>\n<ul><li>诊断: 在商品期货中，净主买占比是动量信号而非反转信号</li>\n<li>行动: 将 <code>scale</code> 从 -2.0 改为 +2.0（高OI做多），同时加入 <code>sym_rolling_ic_gate</code> 过滤弱品种，增加Level2真实买卖量对比</li>\n<li>效果: Sharpe从0.15跃升至1.39，所有gate通过。5个变体Sharpe&gt;0.8</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>R3</strong> -- 参数网格搜索 + 归一化扩展</p>\n<ul><li>诊断: R2最优变体hold_days=5换手过高(6.2/日)，探索更长持仓期和离散LS信号</li>\n<li>行动: 网格搜索 hold_days=[5,10,20] x lookback=[5,10,20] x mode=[cont,ls]，共14个变体 x 3种归一化 = 42个变体</li>\n<li>效果: 确认 oi_bvc_5_h5_raw 仍是最优；CS归一化(1.34)和离散LS(1.27)也表现优异。较长持仓期Sharpe降低但换手率降低</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 需要1分钟K线数据计算BVC，最终因子为日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货（~70个品种），Level2数据可提供额外对比</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 短周期因子（5日回望）效果最强，持有5天换仓</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 换手率较高（日均6.2），适合低交易成本环境\n<p>- BVC的t分布CDF使用近似公式，与精确值有微小偏差 - 因子在股票和商品市场方向相反（股票反转 vs 商品动量），跨资产应用需注意方向 - 短回望窗口(5日)可能在流动性较差的品种上信号质量不稳定</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 35.77s</li>\n</ul>"}